    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Necromantic energies fill a wounds of a creature you can see to further increase their suffering.   The target must make a Constitution saving throw, suffering [[/r 4d4]] + your spellcasting ability modifier necrotic damage on a failed save, or half as much on a successful save. If the damage was dealt to the target by a critical hit then they make the Constitution saving throw at disadvantage.</p><p>A creature can only take damage for this spell once per turn.</p><p><strong>At Higher Levels.</strong> When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, increase the necrotic damage by [[/r 2d4]] for each slot level above 2nd.</p>",
